name: Westside Farmers Market at Cool Spring Park
listing_desc:
West Side Grows Together is a coalition of  residents, businesses, churches, and local leadership working together to transform & strengthen our community.

Our weekly farmers market is a community-based initiative to promote access to the best local produce, grass-fed meats, bakery goods, and much more! We are located at the historic Cool Spring Park. Held every Wednesday from 3:30-6:30 pm, STARTING JUNE 15th through October. 

*Accepting WIC, SFMNP, SNAP, and EBT 

CHECK OUT OUR FARMERS MARKET FACEBOOK PAGE @coolspringfarmersmarket
